Name: Fast Cubes
About the game: Fast Cubes is a puzzle game with time limits. At each level, the player must place the cubes in their respective places before the time counter reaches zero. With new mechanincs every 10 levels, you will have a lot of fun. Features 65 levels to play and have fun. Diverse mechanics.
